data.meta_description: Chris's Library - Free ebook download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read book online for free. This document appears to be a music library containing 10137 songs from various artists totaling 27.9 days or 47.05 GB of music. It lists the song name, time, artist, album, genre, and rating for each track. The library contains a large collection of songs from the band ABBA across multiple albums as well as songs from other classic rock artists like AC/DC.
